This file explains what you can and cannot do with our code, or in other words, the LICENSE file for your tiny brain <3

Make sure you FORK this project using the fork feature, makes your life easier, trust me.

When using our code:
- You must make it known it is based off of our code
- Disclose your source / Make it public
- Keep the same license
- Give us permission to use your code in our codebase
- Credit us

The reason we encourage the use of the fork feature is it handles all of the above requirements for you.
